cast.overview: Katie, a 17-year-old, has been sheltered since childhood and confined to her house during the day by a rare disease that makes even the smallest amount of sunlight deadly. Fate intervenes when she meets Charlie and they embark on a summer romance.
cast.title: Midnight Sun

details.biography: Jaeda Lily Miller, born on October 18, 2006, is an exceptional television and voice actress. She has done so much for her career and has not let her age limit her. Her passion for acting began at an early age, and she decided that she would pursue it and make a career out of it.
details.name: Jaeda Lily Miller
